  <voice name="en-US-JennyNeural">
    <prosody rate="+21%">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful" styledegree="0.9">
      <prosody rate="+5%">
        Absolutely!
      </prosody>
    </mstts:express-as>
     I've been skiing for years, but I feel like I'm still just you know,
    <prosody rate="-5%">
      hoping for the best on every turn.
    </prosody>
       </prosody>
  </voice>

  <voice name="en-US-GuyNeural">
    <prosody rate="+23%">
    <mstts:express-as style="cheerful" styledegree="1.1">
      <prosody pitch="+12%">Ha!</prosody>
       </mstts:express-as>
    I love that honesty.
     Well, today we're going to change that.
     We're going to break down the <emphasis level="moderate">three core concepts</emphasis>
